[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":293},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fwindows\u002F20241004\u002F850567104\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fwindows\u002F20241004\u002F850567104\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fwindows\u002F20241004\u002F850567104\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fwindows\u002F20241004\u002F850567104\u002F":279,"related:\u002Fwindows\u002F20241004\u002F850567104\u002F":288},"\u002Fen\u002Fwindows\u002F2024\u002F10\u002F04\u002Fburn-windows-iso-from-macos\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":115,"date":261,"description":262,"extension":263,"lang":264,"meta":265,"navigation":266,"path":267,"readingMinutes":268,"seo":269,"standalone":270,"stem":271,"tags":272,"tldr":276,"updated":261,"url":277,"__hash__":278},"content\u002FWindows\u002F用-MacOS-燒錄-Windows-作業系統（ISO-檔案）.md","用 MacOS 燒錄 Windows 作業系統（ISO 檔案）","850567104",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":250},"minimark",[11,19,23,26,30,33,43,49,55,64,68,71,78,81,87,90,96,101,104,108,111,117,120,126,130,133,156,159,165,168,191,194,213,216,222,225,246],[12,13,14],"p",{},[15,16],"img",{"alt":17,"src":18},"Windows ISO","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fwindows\u002Fmac-iso-windows\u002F_8bdaf450-56ad-46b3-b516-d0ac546d4a03.jpg",[20,21,22],"h2",{"id":22},"前言",[12,24,25],{},"最近家裡剛好一台 Windows 需要重灌，剛好主要使用的電腦是 Mac，所以就來寫一篇文章來介紹如何在 Mac 上燒錄 Windows 作業系統（ISO 檔案）。",[20,27,29],{"id":28},"windows-作業系統","Windows 作業系統",[12,31,32],{},"首先我們可以從 Windows 官方網站取得 Windows 作業系統的 ISO 檔案，這邊我們會以 Windows 10 為例哩～",[12,34,35,36],{},"下載點：",[37,38,42],"a",{"href":39,"rel":40},"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.microsoft.com\u002Fzh-tw\u002Fsoftware-download\u002Fwindows10ISO",[41],"nofollow","Windows 10 下載頁面",[12,44,45],{},[15,46],{"alt":47,"src":48},"Windows 10","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fwindows\u002Fmac-iso-windows\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202024-10-04%2012.32.56.png",[12,50,51],{},[52,53,54],"strong",{},"本篇不會提供 Windows 金鑰。",[56,57,58],"blockquote",{},[12,59,60,63],{},[52,61,62],{},"Note","\nISO 是一種光碟封存檔案的格式，概念上就是把一張光碟的內容打包成一個檔案，所以我們可以透過燒錄軟體來將 ISO 檔案寫入光碟中。",[20,65,67],{"id":66},"格式化-usb-隨身碟","格式化 USB 隨身碟",[12,69,70],{},"接下來請準備一個至少 64GB 以上的 USB 隨身碟，然後我們要先做一件很重要的事情，也就是格式化 USB 隨身碟。",[56,72,73],{},[12,74,75,77],{},[52,76,62],{},"\n格式化用途在於確保 USB 隨身碟是乾淨的，這樣才能確保燒錄的 Windows 作業系統是正確的。",[12,79,80],{},"請先插入 USB 隨身碟，然後桌面上應該可以看到隨身硬碟，點它右鍵選擇「清除硬碟」",[12,82,83],{},[15,84],{"alt":85,"src":86},"清除硬碟","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fwindows\u002Fmac-iso-windows\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202024-10-04%2013.10.11.png",[12,88,89],{},"接著清除硬碟時，選擇「ExFAT」格式，然後點擊「清除」 即可",[12,91,92],{},[15,93],{"alt":94,"src":95},"ExFAT","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fwindows\u002Fmac-iso-windows\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202024-10-04%2013.10.19.png",[97,98,100],"h3",{"id":99},"exfat-vs-ms-dos-fat","ExFAT vs MS-DOS (FAT)",[12,102,103],{},"MS-DOS 是比較老舊的格式",[20,105,107],{"id":106},"掛載-windows-作業系統","掛載 Windows 作業系統",[12,109,110],{},"點擊剛剛下載的 Windows 10 ISO 檔案兩下，Mac 就會自動虛擬光碟機掛載 Windows 10 的 ISO 檔案，這時候你應該可以在桌面看到掛載的 Windows 10",[12,112,113],{},[15,114],{"alt":115,"src":116},"Windows","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fwindows\u002Fmac-iso-windows\u002F202410041315.jpg",[12,118,119],{},"點開後，可以看到裡面有一堆檔案，這就是 Windows 10 的安裝檔案",[12,121,122],{},[15,123],{"alt":124,"src":125},"Windows 檔案","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fwindows\u002Fmac-iso-windows\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202024-10-04%2013.16.46.png",[20,127,129],{"id":128},"燒錄-windows-作業系統","燒錄 Windows 作業系統",[12,131,132],{},"接下來請打開終端機（在此示範用 iTerm2），並輸入以下指令：",[134,135,140],"pre",{"className":136,"code":137,"language":138,"meta":139,"style":139},"language-bash shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","diskutil list\n","bash","",[141,142,143],"code",{"__ignoreMap":139},[144,145,148,152],"span",{"class":146,"line":147},"line",1,[144,149,151],{"class":150},"s_sBn","diskutil",[144,153,155],{"class":154},"sTRMh"," list\n",[12,157,158],{},"這個指令意思是指列出所有的硬碟，這樣我們就可以知道 USB 隨身碟的裝置名稱，以我的 USB 為例就是「UFDRecovery」",[12,160,161],{},[15,162],{"alt":163,"src":164},"diskutil list","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fwindows\u002Fmac-iso-windows\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202024-10-04%2013.22.34.png",[12,166,167],{},"接著輸入以下指令來準備燒錄 Windows 作業系統：",[134,169,171],{"className":136,"code":170,"language":138,"meta":139,"style":139},"cp -rp \u002FVolumes\u002FISO虛擬碟名稱\u002F* \u002FVolumes\u002Fusb隨身碟名稱\u002F\n",[141,172,173],{"__ignoreMap":139},[144,174,175,178,182,185,188],{"class":146,"line":147},[144,176,177],{"class":150},"cp",[144,179,181],{"class":180},"sCcAr"," -rp",[144,183,184],{"class":154}," \u002FVolumes\u002FISO虛擬碟名稱\u002F",[144,186,187],{"class":180},"*",[144,189,190],{"class":154}," \u002FVolumes\u002Fusb隨身碟名稱\u002F\n",[12,192,193],{},"以我的為例子就是以下：",[134,195,197],{"className":136,"code":196,"language":138,"meta":139,"style":139},"cp -rp \u002FVolumes\u002FWindows10\u002F* \u002FVolumes\u002FUFDRecovery\u002F\n",[141,198,199],{"__ignoreMap":139},[144,200,201,203,205,208,210],{"class":146,"line":147},[144,202,177],{"class":150},[144,204,181],{"class":180},[144,206,207],{"class":154}," \u002FVolumes\u002FWindows10\u002F",[144,209,187],{"class":180},[144,211,212],{"class":154}," \u002FVolumes\u002FUFDRecovery\u002F\n",[12,214,215],{},"Enter 後，就會開始複製 Windows 10 的安裝檔案到 USB 隨身碟中，這個過程可能會花一點時間哩～",[12,217,218],{},[15,219],{"alt":220,"src":221},"跑完結果","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fwindows\u002Fmac-iso-windows\u002F202410041329.jpg",[12,223,224],{},"跑完之後，就會變成以下這樣（ps. 它並不會出現任何提示，只要跑完就代表完成了）",[56,226,227],{},[12,228,229,231,233,234,237,238,241,242,245],{},[52,230,62],{},[141,232,177],{}," 意思是指複製檔案，",[141,235,236],{},"-rp"," 是指遞迴複製，所以 ",[141,239,240],{},"\u002FVolumes\u002FWindows10\u002F*"," 是指 Windows 10 的安裝檔案透過遞迴複製到 ",[141,243,244],{},"\u002FVolumes\u002FUFDRecovery\u002F"," 中。",[247,248,249],"style",{},"html pre.shiki code .s_sBn, html code.shiki .s_sBn{--shiki-default:#FFB757}html pre.shiki code .sTRMh, html code.shiki .sTRMh{--shiki-default:#ADDCFF}html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html pre.shiki code .sCcAr, html code.shiki .sCcAr{--shiki-default:#91CBFF}",{"title":139,"searchDepth":251,"depth":251,"links":252},2,[253,254,255,259,260],{"id":22,"depth":251,"text":22},{"id":28,"depth":251,"text":29},{"id":66,"depth":251,"text":67,"children":256},[257],{"id":99,"depth":258,"text":100},3,{"id":106,"depth":251,"text":107},{"id":128,"depth":251,"text":129},"2024-10-04 11:47:14","家裡 Windows 要重灌但手邊只有 Mac？這一篇手把手帶你在 macOS 上做 Windows 10 安裝 USB：USB 格式選 ExFAT 還是 MS-DOS、 ISO 從哪載、燒錄流程一次講清楚。","md","zh-Hant",{},true,"\u002Fwindows\u002Fmacos-windows-iso","2",{"title":6,"description":262},false,"Windows\u002F用-MacOS-燒錄-Windows-作業系統（ISO-檔案）",[273,115,274,275],"macOS","燒錄","ISO",null,"\u002Fwindows\u002F20241004\u002F850567104\u002F","7y7dbGiy6pvCdhlXYwmEPy0p3jyfvqUOAEWHRb7w49o",{"newer":280,"older":284},{"url":281,"title":282,"date":283},"\u002Flearnexp\u002F20241205\u002F2148986526\u002F","發生車禍了怎麼辦？ - 事故處理 - 1","2024-12-05 20:01:26",{"url":285,"title":286,"date":287},"\u002FTypeScript\u002F20240930\u002F1917741270\u002F","掌握 TypeScript 泛型（Generics） & Vue3 泛型","2024-09-30 17:31:32",[289],{"url":290,"title":291,"date":292,"readingMinutes":268},"\u002Fwindows\u002F20240324\u002F4257487202\u002F","你知道嗎？Windows 的關機並不是真的關機","2024-03-24 13:46:56",1784020409532]